@section Landing{
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/Landing.css">
}

<header id="landing-header">
    <div class="wrapper nav landing-nav" data-aos="fade-down">
        <div class="logo">
            <a asp-action="LandingPage" asp-controller="Home">
                <h1 class="abril">Together</h1>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <a href="#how">How it Works</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a asp-action="Login" asp-controller="Home">Login</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a asp-action="SelectRole" asp-controller="Home" id="register-btn" class="standout-btn">Register</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<section id="banner">
    <div id="leftCol" class="col">
        <div class="banner-text" data-aos="fade-right">
            <h1 class="abril">IN THIS TOGETHER</h1>
            <p>A platform where people can seek help to purchase or pick-up items when they're uncapable and those that are able to help, can offer their time to obtain the items that others can't</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col image"></div>
</section>

<section id="how" class="wrapper" data-aos="fade-down">
    <h3 class="abril">How It Works</h3>
    <div class="cards">

        <div class="card">
            <p>This platform was built with the intention to help out people who are incapable to leave their homes to purchase groceries or home  essentials. With the experience of COVID-19, we realize that this platform will be essential to those who are in quarantine, a senior person or handicapped.</p>
            <p>With <span class="bold">Together</span>, you will be able to register as a person who needs help or you can register as a helper. The person in need can then fill out a form of the items that they require specifying how urgent is their request.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585559605688-6374ebdc7078?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=3150&q=80" class="pic">
        </div>

    </div>
</section>